title: Minor ReadMe Update
body:
Two sentences read a little awkward, so I tweaked them.
 
1) "Design patterns are **formalized best practices that the** programmer can use" -> "Design patterns are **the best formalized practices a** programmer can use"
2) "Reusing design patterns **helps to prevent subtle issues that can** cause major" -> "Reusing design patterns **help prevent subtle issues which** cause major

Hope this helps!

title: Game loop
body:
Implementation of various interchangeable Game Loops.

The game loop pattern allows state and render to be updated in a loop. Based on the implementation, this can be together or independently.

Issue #551 

Implementation includes:

- Swing display and game state
- Interchangeable loops
- Descriptions of loops in README
- UML Diagram
